Initial reports were received that one woman was wounded. A www.mobserver.co.za journalist is currently at the hospital and can confirm that five police vehicles are on the scene and that entrance into the hospital is being denied. Civilians who were at the hospital are systematically being let go. This is a developing story and more updates will follow. Anyone with information regarding the incident is asked to please call the Middelburg Observer standby number on 072 248 3855. 